AGI - "However, this is a symbolic day, because Francesco Schiavone was a charismatic leader.> His choice of repentance will be reflected also on the arrangement of current organized crime in Casertano and not only. His figure has a symbolic weight even if the scenarios of the house chamorra are profoundly changed and we do not know how much his image in the criminal context still has value." Raffaello&nbsp;Magi, > from 2013 advisor to the Court of Cassation, in 1998 he was in the judiciary college of the Court of Assisi of Santa Maria Capua Vetere, chaired by Catello Marano, who passed to history not only judicial with the name of the investigation that gave him life, Spartacus; and it is also the extremist of the more than 3,500 pages of the sentence that for the first time nailed and made known the leadership of that clan of Casalesi>, including Sandokan, whose military and economic power was known until then only to the 'addicts to the works'. "The trial began on 11 July and I in May had questioned Rebibbia Schiavone, who was latitante since 1995 and in May had been recently arrested - he recalls the judge&nbsp;Magi&nbsp; speaking with the AGI&nbsp;- his line of defense was to contest everything he was written, to proclaim himself a passionate buffalo maneuver framed by repentant. Luciano Violante was then president of Antimafia and after the death of Don Diana had had harsh words for the Casalesi. In the ruling of Spartacus, we have committed his first ergastol to the boss, although he had already been sentenced to lower penises. And there were 12 murders we attributed to him in Spartacus, including that of Antonio Bardellino, for us in May 1988, although the body was never found; a quadruple murder of cutolians; and others in the internal feud with the De Falco, started in 1991 with the killing of Vincenzo De Falco and ended in 1994". &nbsp;
&nbsp;
What can Schiavone tell the magistrates? "Two aspects are important to his collaboration, if it were verified as true - replies&nbsp;Magi&nbsp;- the first, the network of relations of the clan prior to his arrest, those between 1993 and 1998, years in which he was the head of the dome, relationships that are not told at the lower levels with the worlds of the enterprise and the institutions, a network more reserved and held in the knowledge only of the bosses. In this way we would have a historical memory. The other aspect is a verification of the prison regime. It would allow us to understand whether, despite the 41 bis, he had contacts with people outside >ed managed or not to orientate the operational strategies of Casalesi. A kind of 41 bis operation test. Moreover, it is possible that economic relations created by him are still existing. On the plane of military strategy and murders almost all aspects were deepened by trials." "It would be interesting to understand - the magistrate continues - whether or not he gave instructions to Giuseppe Setola (the superkiller, then arrested and tried, ndr.) for the massacres of 2008, a short distance from the conclusion in Appeal of the Spartacus process", he emphasizes. It remains also for&nbsp;Magi&nbsp; the surprise of this repentance >, which did not even record when the son and his cousin decided to collaborate: "It has always been an irreducible, > has always tried to discredit repented figures. I couldn't imagine his collaboration. The reasons can be the most varied. One aspect could be related to concerns for children still in freedom perhaps for choices of paths similar to his. Or the struggle of the prison along with the advanced age and the desire to be in the final part of its existence closer to its affections, perhaps because its personality is now flawed". &nbsp;

